[["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/span[1]/text()[1]","WAYNE COUNTY, MS (WDAM) -\n            "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[1]/text()[1]","Wayne County triple-homicide suspect Willie Miller made his initial appearance in Wayne County Justice Court Thursday. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/h3[1]/span[1]/text()[1]","MORE"],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/h3[1]/span[2]/text()[1]","Additional Links"],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/div[1]/div[1]/div[1]/h3[1]/span[3]/text()[1]","Poll"],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/div[1]/div[1]/text()[1]"," "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[2]/text()[1]","Miller is facing three counts of murder with bond set at $1 million per count. Miller is also facing one count of sexual battery with a $500,000 bond. He was charged with a felony of malicious mischief with a bond of $300,000. He was also charged with possession of a firearm by a convicted felon and arson to the third-degree. Those bonds were respectively set at $300,000 and $500,000. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[3]/strong[1]/text()[1]","The confession:"],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[4]/text()[1]","Investigator Jamey Beard with the Wayne County Sheriff's Department said Miller had an altercation with two male victims in a Jeep. Miller then shot both suspects, and drove their bodies to the home of Sonya Taylor. According to Miller's open courtroom confession, he shot the two men in the head. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[5]/text()[1]","According to Investigator Beard, a witness to the crime lived with Taylor. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[6]/text()[1]","Miller told a courtroom Thursday that he entered the home and shot Taylor in the head."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[7]/text()[1]","Investigator Beard said Miller then forced the witness in the home to have sexual relations with him. Beard said the woman consented because she feared for her life. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[8]/text()[1]","Beard said Miller then made the witness drive him and the bodies in the Jeep to a separate location so he could torch the truck. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[9]/text()[1]","It is unclear at this time why Miller chose to shoot Taylor, or why he made the witness have sexual relations with him. Beard said that Taylor and the witness were related. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[10]/text()[1]","Beard questioned the witness, but there are no charges pending against her. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[11]/text()[1]","After Beard spoke in court, Judge Charles Chapman asked Miller why he allegedly did it."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[12]/text()[1]","Miller then admitted that he made a big mistake and he was on crystal meth and Lortabs the night before and of the murders.  "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[13]/text()[1]","He also said that the two men were making fun of him, which is why he shot them. After that, Miller said he blacked out. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[14]/strong[1]/text()[1]","The capture:"],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[15]/text()[1]","Miller was taken into custody Wednesday in connection to a triple homicide in Wayne County."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[16]/text()[1]","He was found in Wayne County around 7:30 a.m. Wednesday morning. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[17]/text()[1]","Officers closed in on Miller on Boyle Road in the beat four community of Wayne County. He was then taken into custody by officers and was transported to a local emergency room to be treated for minor cuts he sustained in the woods. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[18]/text()[1]","According to MBI, Miller was taken into custody less than a mile from where he ditched the vehicle and ran. During the night, authorities located his shoes and hat as they followed a blood trail."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[19]/text()[1]","Miller was arrested wearing a pair of shorts, but authorities were unable to locate his shirt during the manhunt. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[20]/strong[1]/text()[1]","The scene: "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[21]/text()[1]","Authorities confirmed three people were killed in Wayne County on Tuesday."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[22]/text()[1]","According to MBI, one victim is identified as Sonya Taylor, 41. MBI said she was killed at 353 Denham Progress Road and she was found around 11:30 a.m. Tuesday."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[23]/text()[1]","Two other victims were burned in a truck, that was found around 4:40 p.m. on a side road off Denham Progress Road. MBI waited on a positive identification for the release of the names because the two bodies were burned beyond recognition."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[24]/text()[1]","According to MBI Spokesperson Warren Strain, officers spent all night pursuing the suspect in the Beat 4 community off Hwy 84 where they believe he was hiding in a wooded area. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[26]/text()[1]","Strain added that the Mississippi Highway Patrol helicopter assisted in the manhunt."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[27]/text()[1]","Authorities said the suspect was armed and fled from his vehicle into a wooded area earlier Tuesday after police began the initial pursuit. "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[2]/div[3]/div[2]/div[2]/div[3]/p[28]/text()[1]","Mississippi Bureau of Investigations and Mississippi Highway Patrol was on the scene, and the MBI crime scene unit was processing the scene. "]]